data.description: $5000.00 Seller concession with full price offer (i.e. closing cost, cosmetic repairs/paint/floor) Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, strategically located near All American Hwy for quick access to Ft. Liberty and 295. The inviting foyer welcomes you into the heart of the home—a laminated living room with an electric fireplace, creating a warm ambiance for gatherings. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, spacious layout, a generous walk-in closet, separate toilet, walk-in shower, and a garden tub. Two additional bedrooms and 2nd bath are on the opposite side, offering privacy and convenience. Upstairs, a finished bonus room. The 2-car garage for your vehicles also serves as a fitness haven, gym equipment and a hanging punching bag. Experience the perfect blend of style and functionality, allowing for seamless flow and ample natural light. This residence is a testament to contemporary design, ensuring a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out, see it today!
